Name: Rover-Havoc
Desc: A mysterious Resonator with the power to absorb all sounds. Currently journeying to find their lost memories.

CharaInfo.Info: A mysterious Resonator with the power to absorb all sounds. Currently journeying to find their lost memories.

Voices.Title: Idle: II
Voices.Content: This is a testament to my connection with the world around me, and it's very much my companion now, bearing witness to everything I've experienced on this journey.

Voices.Title: Idle: III
Voices.Content: It is natural to feel dreadful of the unknown, yet... there are times when the unknown harbors hope, like how I can never know what else this power has to offer.

Voices.Title: Join Team: I
Voices.Content: We still have a long journey ahead of us. Let's press on.

Voices.Title: Join Team: III
Voices.Content: I will be there for everyone... As we head toward our shared future, leaving the past behind.

Voices.Title: Ascension: I
Voices.Content: The world around me... I can hear it clearer now.

Voices.Title: Ascension: II
Voices.Content: This power... it's mysterious, yet reassuring nonetheless.

Voices.Title: Ascension: III
Voices.Content: I still need more time to acquaint myself with this unfamiliar world.

Voices.Title: Ascension: IV
Voices.Content: A new journey awaits? Brimming with novel sounds, stories, and... fragmented memories.

Voices.Title: Ascension: V
Voices.Content: The place where the land ends is where the ocean begins. Our journey is far from ending.

Skill.Name: Tuneslayer
Skill.Desc:
<size=40><color=Title>Basic Attack</color></size>
Rover-Havoc performs up to 5 consecutive attacks, dealing <color=Dark>Havoc DMG</color>.
<size=10> </size>
<size=40><color=Title>Heavy Attack</color></size>
Rover-Havoc consumes STA to attack, dealing <color=Dark>Havoc DMG</color>.
Use <color=Highlight>Basic Attack</color> after casting Heavy Attack to cast Basic Attack 4.
<size=10> </size>
<size=40><color=Title>Mid-air Attack</color></size>
Rover-Havoc consumes STA to cast a Mid-Air Plunging Attack, dealing <color=Dark>Havoc DMG</color>.
<size=10> </size>
<size=40><color=Title>Dodge Counter</color></size>
Use <color=Highlight>Basic Attack</color> after a successful Dodge to attack the target, dealing <color=Dark>Havoc DMG</color>.

Skill.Name: Wingblade
Skill.Desc: Transform sound into feathers, dealing <color=Dark>Havoc DMG</color>.

Skill.Name: Deadening Abyss
Skill.Desc: Rover gathers resonating sounds to attack a target, dealing <color=Dark>Havoc DMG</color>.

Skill.Name: Metamorph
Skill.Desc: In the <color=Highlight>Dark Surge</color> state, Havoc DMG Bonus is increased by {0}.

Skill.Name: Bleak Crescendo
Skill.Desc: While in the <color=Highlight>Dark Surge</color> state, <color=Highlight>Basic Attack</color> recovers {0} extra Resonance Energy when it hits a target, and this effect can be triggered 1 time per second.

Skill.Name: Umbra Eclipse
Skill.Desc:
<size=40><color=Title>Devastation</color></size>
When "Umbra" is full, hold <color=Highlight>Basic Attack</color> to cast <color=Highlight>Devastation</color> to attack the target, dealing <color=Dark>Havoc DMG</color>, considered as Heavy Attack DMG.
<size=10> </size>
<size=40><color=Title>Dark Surge</color></size>
After casting <color=Highlight>Devastation</color>, Rover enters the <color=Highlight>Dark Surge</color> state. In this state:
<color=Highlight>Basic Attack</color> is replaced with <color=Highlight>Enhanced Basic Attack</color>, which performs up to 5 consecutive attacks, dealing <color=Dark>Havoc DMG</color>.
<color=Highlight>Heavy Attack</color> is replaced with <color=Highlight>Enhanced Heavy Attack</color>;
Use <color=Highlight>Basic Attack</color> after casting <color=Highlight>Enhanced Heavy Attack</color> to cast Heavy Attack <color=Highlight>Thwackblade</color> to attack the target, dealing <color=Dark>Havoc DMG</color>, considered as Heavy Attack DMG.
Use <color=Highlight>Basic Attack</color> after casting Heavy Attack <color=Highlight>Thwackblade</color> to cast <color=Highlight> Enhanced Basic Attack 3</color> to attack the target, dealing <color=Dark>Havoc DMG</color>;
Resonance Skill <color=Highlight>Wingblade</color> is replaced with Resonance Skill <color=Highlight>Lifetaker</color>, transforming sounds into blades to attack the target, dealing <color=Dark>Havoc DMG</color>.
<size=10> </size>
<size=40><color=Title>Umbra</color></size>
Rover can hold up to 100 points of Umbra.
Normal Attack <color=Highlight>Tuneslayer</color> recovers Umbra on hit.
Resonance Skill <color=Highlight>Wingblade</color> recovers Umbra when cast.
Resonance Skill <color=Highlight>Lifetaker</color> recovers Umbra when cast.
Intro Skill <color=Highlight>Instant of Annihilation</color> recovers Umbra when cast.

Skill.Name: Soundweaver
Skill.Desc: Rover summons a Havoc Field, dealing <color=Dark>Havoc DMG</color> of {1} of Rover's ATK to all targets within the range every {0}s for {2}s.

6.Desc: In the <color=Highlight>Dark Surge</color> state, Rover's Crit. Rate is increased by {0}.
